der parent, Set<String> rejectedClassNames) {\n            super(parent);\n            this.rejectedClassNames = rejectedClassNames;\n        }\n\n[94 more lines in file. Use offset=161 to continue.]"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1779501738969}]}
